         <OBJECT_CONTRACT ITEM="1">
            <TITLE>
               <P>Learning Disability Intensive Support Service</P>
            </TITLE>
            <CPV_MAIN>
               <CPV_CODE CODE="85000000"/>
            </CPV_MAIN>
            <SHORT_DESCR>
               <P>Aberdeen City Council requires the provision of an Intensive Support Service, commissioned by the Learning Disability Service within Aberdeen City Health &amp; Social Care Partnership. The service will provide immediate, intensive and robust support to individuals and services within the learning disability service which are facing impending crisis or significant change.</P>
               <P>The service will be registered with the care inspectorate as a care at home and housing support service and will hold a suitable registration to provide direct support to individuals from aged 16 years.</P>
               <P>The intensive support service will be available 24 hours a day, 7 days a week, 365 days a year. The service will operate a mix of direct support delivery and on call support.</P>
            </SHORT_DESCR>
            <VAL_ESTIMATED_TOTAL CURRENCY="GBP">1500000.00</VAL_ESTIMATED_TOTAL>
            <NO_LOT_DIVISION/>
            <OBJECT_DESCR ITEM="1">
               <CPV_ADDITIONAL>
                  <CPV_CODE CODE="85000000"/>
               </CPV_ADDITIONAL>
               <n2016:NUTS CODE="UKM50"/>
               <MAIN_SITE>
                  <P>Aberdeen City.</P>
               </MAIN_SITE>
               <SHORT_DESCR>
                  <P>The intensive support service will provide immediate, intensive and robust support to individuals and services within the learning disability service which are facing impending crisis or significant change. The service will be available 24 hours a day, 7 days a week, 365 days a year. The service will operate a mix of direct support delivery and on call support.</P>
                  <P>Direct support may include the provision of personal care, personal support and housing support. Support may be delivered in a person’s own home /family home, in formal care settings, in clinical settings or in the community.</P>
                  <P>An on call system will be operated as part of the service and may be delivered in part via telephone or technology based support and in part by direct delivery of care and support.</P>
                  <P>Services will be delivered in all areas of Aberdeen.</P>
               </SHORT_DESCR>
               <VAL_OBJECT CURRENCY="GBP">1500000</VAL_OBJECT>
               <DATE_START>2018-10-01</DATE_START>
               <DATE_END>2021-09-30</DATE_END>
               <NO_EU_PROGR_RELATED/>
               <INFO_ADD>
                  <P>The contract will be for an initial three year period with 2 optional 1 year extensions. Dates and values provided are for duration of initial contract.</P>
               </INFO_ADD>
            </OBJECT_DESCR>
         </OBJECT_CONTRACT>
